      "filePath": "docs/api.md",
      "summary": "Comprehensive API reference documenting all three protocol formats (OpenAI, Anthropic Messages, Google Gemini) exposed by the gateway, including authentication, model suffixes, thinking modes, tool calling, image/video generation, admin endpoints, and error response formats.",
